  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<h3>About the Role</h3><p>We are seeking an experienced <strong>Senior Sales Consultant</strong> to drive business development, manage key client relationships, and deliver tailored consultancy solutions to corporate clients. This role is suited for a commercially driven professional who combines strong sales execution with consultative thinking and long-term relationship building.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><ul><li>Identify, develop, and close new business opportunities across target industries</li><li>Build and manage a robust sales pipeline from lead generation to deal closure</li><li>Conduct client meetings to understand business needs and propose customised solutions</li><li>Meet or exceed individual and team sales targets</li><li>Serve as a trusted advisor to clients, maintaining long-term relationship</li><li>Analyse client requirements and recommend appropriate consultancy or workforce solution</li><li>Prepare and present proposals, quotations, and contracts</li></ul></p><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>3–5 years of sales or business development experience</strong>, preferably in consultancy, manpower, recruitment, or professional services</p></li><li><p>Proven track record of meeting or exceeding sales targets</p></li><li><p>Strong consultative selling and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and presentation abilities</p></li><li><p>Ability to engage senior stakeholders and decision-makers</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Business, Marketing, Human Resources, or related field preferred<br /></p><p><strong>WOLA Recruitment Pte Ltd</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 23C1703</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel: Thea Cheah</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel Reg No: R23118878</strong></p></li></ul>",
